    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“(...) 几个世纪以来，恐怖故事一直与男人形影不离。它们形式不一，种类丰富。<u>但它们为何而存在？</u>？为什么我们会如此享受恐惧？在此次<strong>治疗</strong>期间，我会尝试 (...)”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（选自<strong>埃默森博士的诊所</strong>传单）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361560/extras/d1d6035b2ad8a6e0a121f5cb213f2d1e.avif?t=1770217453\" width=620 height=151 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>尝试我们将文学带入互动媒介的原创方法。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入怪奇小说和宇宙恐怖杰作的世界。在完全尊重作者意愿，<strong>完整未删减的版本中</strong>尽情体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361560/extras/a4a61cb77f293c9e8531134cb88b0859.avif?t=1770217453\" width=620 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>《Dr.Emmerson's Nocturnes》</i>是一款全语音实时3D视觉小说游戏[/b]。如果你对这个概念感兴趣，我们强烈建议你看看我们备受好评且<u>完全免费</u>的<strong>《大衮》</strong>改编版，这是H·P·洛夫克拉夫特所著的首个克苏鲁神话相关故事：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361560/extras/1a6c736d0d535958d159fa2f62945e36.avif?t=1770217453\" width=460 height=214 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-- <strong>收入的15%</strong>将会捐赠给<strong>慈善机构</strong> --</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（由我们的Discord社区选择）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特色：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 全语音实时3D<strong>叙事体验</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 支持<strong>VR</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>3-4个故事</strong>（可能会更多 - 埃默森博士经常会调整他的治疗方法）由包括<strong>H.P·洛夫克拉夫特</strong>和<strong>Stefan Grabiński</strong>在内的最佳怪奇小说作者创作</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 游戏中隐藏着数十个关于作者及其著作的<strong>趣事</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361560/extras/f0d62c3e91bae5c2d43fce8cf93e3331.avif?t=1770217453\" width=620 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所以放轻松，让埃默森博士带你穿越<strong>恐惧的所有颜色</strong>。别怕，这些都只是故事而已，不会伤害到你。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>?吗此如是真</strong></i></h2>",
